verbose_text: However, LdMC2 does not appear in the TriTryp database (https://tritrypdb.org/tritrypdb/), it has the same sequence as LmjF.35.1580 and experiments have been done with LdMC1 or LdMC antibodies that do not discriminate between both proteins, raising the question of the nature of LdMC2.
evidence: LdMC antibodies that do not discriminate between both proteins, raising the question of the nature of LdMC2
